<HEADLINE> Galaxy 5, Wizards 1  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   KANSAS CITY, Mo. (AP) -- Mauricio Cienfuegos had two goals and an
assist as the Los Angeles Galaxy beat Kansas City 5-1 Saturday to
close within four points of the first-place Wizards in MLS' Western
Division.
