<HEADLINE> Uncharted Haven Wins San Clemente  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   DEL MAR, Calif. (AP) -- Uncharted Haven rallied from the rear
halfway through the $150,000 San Clemente Handicap to win by one
length at Del Mar on Saturday night.
